headline: Corridor Platforms and Oliver Wyman Launch Responsible AI Sandbox with Google Cloud
summary: NEW YORK, July 23, 2025--Corridor Platforms, Oliver Wyman, and Google Cloud launch the first industry-led Responsible AI Sandbox to help enterprises deploy GenAI at scale.
